summary: This is an email forwarding the 'Child Exploitation & Porn Update Report III' for Project Safe Childhood, instructing Chiefs and the Project Safe Childhood Coordinator to remind assigned Assistant U.S. Attorneys to update their cases.
keyFacts: A 'Child Exploitation & Porn Update Report III' was distributed on February 22, 2021.
The report is part of 'Project Safe Childhood', a federal initiative.
The email instructs Chiefs and a Coordinator to remind assigned Assistant U.S. Attorneys (AUSAs) to update their cases.
The document is an administrative communication regarding case management for child exploitation and pornography cases.
